name: WIZARD2 - Heretic
description: This PWAD was created from the same author who created the WIZARD.WAD level that was in the TiC's WAD reviews (#7), if you played that PWAD, and enjoyed it, perhaps you'll enjoy WIZARD2... try it out, and let me know what you think... thanks. This PWAD was made to play on the (Registered) version of Heretic, it will not play on the (Shareware) version.
